— Reason About the Problem, Audit Once, Don't Narrate the Self\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — should I reconsider whether I reconsidered\\\") is the smell; name it in ≤3 words and return to the problem. | Prioritize when: what it found.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 18040,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/post-implementation-deep-review.md\",\n          \"title\": \"POST-IMPLEMENTATION DEEP-REVIEW — Mandatory after substantive ship\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: asserting new invariant | | Prioritize when: asserting new invariant |\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 18039,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/fable-governor.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Fable-5 Governor — Reason Outward, Act, Commit, Qualify Minimally\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — do not audit the audit. | Prioritize when: the caveat changes what the reader should do — once, in the fewest words.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 18038,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/deep-skill-workflow-required.md\",\n          \"title\": \"DEEP SKILLS — Use the Workflow, Never Hand-Roll\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — Never Hand-Roll\\\" | Prioritize when: Nev