ligns with \\\"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\\\"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16263,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/finding-is-a-hypothesis.md\",\n          \"title\": \"A Finding Is a Hypothesis Until You Open the Cited Code\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — never ground truth. | Prioritize when: only verdict discipline still holds: never soften an active blocker without new evidence.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 15815,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/regression-baseline-and-delta.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Baseline Before No-Regressions; Report the Delta\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — never a grep narrowed to your own files — and report the delta in the form `baseline N failing {…} → now M: {…}`. | Prioritize when: never re-renders, a screenshot of the wrong screen, a fixture older than your work making a green result suspect. \\\"No r…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 15814,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/main-branch-direct-push.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Main Branch — Owner's AIs Push Directly\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — Do NOT default to a feature-branch + PR flow, do NOT re-ask whether to use a PR, and do NOT flag the bypass or the unsi… | Prioritize when: only (the tree often has concurrent parallel-session work + daemon metadata churn — NEVER `git add -A` blindly; use exp…\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"triggered\": [\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7589,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/005-architecture-audit\",\n          \"title\": \"System-Spec-Kit Architecture Audit v2 [system-spec-kit/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/005-architecture-audit/research]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"system\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"research\",\n            \"005\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7426,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/021-spec-kit-phase-system\",\n          \"title\": \"Verification Checklist: SpecKit Phase System [system-spec-kit/021-spec-kit-phase-system/checklist]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"verification\",\n            \"phase\",\n            \"system\",\n            \"021\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7434,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/021-spec-kit-phase-system\",\n          \"title\": \"Feature Specification: SpecKit Phase System [system-spec-kit/021-spec-kit-phase-system/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"phase\",\n            \"system\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"021\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7428,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/021-spec-kit-phase-system\",\n          \"title\": \"Decision Record: SpecKit Phase System [system-spec-kit/021-spec-kit-phase-system/decision-record]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"phase\",\n            \"system\",\n            \"021\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 1498,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"skilled-agent-orchestration/z_archive/024-sk-deep-research-refinement\",\n          \"title\": \"Feature Specification: sk-deep-research Refinement [skilled-agent-orchestration/024-sk-deep-research-refinement/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"deep\",\n            \"research\",\n            \"refinement\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"surfaced_at\": \"2026-06-18T05:42:54.966Z\",\n      \"latencyMs\": 301\n    },\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1781761374566,"end":1781761375104}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_01f16b672c743508016a33855bd2f4819180269d62c8cb58bd"}},"id":"prt_ed940eeae0011kULDuj6YS1v0o","sessionID":"ses_126bff004ffeidXJpk4781In70","messageID":"msg_ed940de98001aIgZ530a3Symqa"}}
